Sodomized - Raised in Meat [Metal] (2015) (mp3)

Sodomized was formed back in 1993 by Eric(fig)Newton-guitar/vokills,Dan Baker-Drums,Joe Baker-Bass.Recorded 1st demo"Sodomize The Corpse"in 1993. Joe switched to guitar Brian Baxter joined on bass in 1994 and recorded 2nd demo"Cannibalistic Devourment".Recorded 3rd demo "Female Genital Mutilation" in 1996 with Scott Cunningham replacing Joe on guitar,although this demo was never officially released.The band called it quits in 1998.Did a reunion show July of 2012 then decided to continue on later that year.Did random shows and then in March of 2015 released first full length CD "Raised In Meat".Currently playing shows to support the new CD and plan on working on new material for future release.
